<h1 id="é›»ç£å¤šé‡æ¥µæ”¾å°„">é›»ç£å¤šé‡æ¥µæ”¾å°„</h1>

<p>ã‚¸ã‚§ãƒ•ã‚£ãƒ¡ãƒ³ã‚³æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã‹ã‚‰ã€ä»»æ„ã®é›»è·åˆ†å¸ƒãƒ»é›»æµåˆ†å¸ƒã«ã‚ˆã‚‹é›»ç£æ”¾å°„ã¯ä»¥ä¸‹ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚</p>

\[\mathbf{E} 
= \iiint \frac{1}{c^2 R} \left( \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right] \times \mathbf{n} \right) \times \mathbf{n}dV \tag{1}\]

\[\mathbf{B} 
= \iiint \frac{1}{c^2R} \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t} \right] \times \mathbf{n} dV \tag{2}\]

<p>ä»¥ä¸‹ã§ã¯ã“ã‚Œã‚’å¤šé‡æ¥µå±•é–‹ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§ã€åŒæ¥µå­æ”¾å°„æˆåˆ†ã¨å››é‡æ¥µå­æ”¾å°„æˆåˆ†ã‚’å°å‡ºã—ã¦ã¿ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="é›»æ°—åŒæ¥µå­æ”¾å°„">é›»æ°—åŒæ¥µå­æ”¾å°„</h2>

<p>ã¾ãšã¯é›»è·ãƒ»é›»æµåˆ†å¸ƒãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹ä½ç½®\(\mathbf{r}_0\)ã‹ã‚‰è¦³æ¸¬è€…ã®ã„ã‚‹ä½ç½®\(\mathbf{r}\)ã¾ã§ã®è·é›¢\(R\)ã«ãŠã„ã¦ã€\(\vert \mathbf{r}_0 \vert \ll \vert \mathbf{r} \vert\)ã¨ã—ã¦ãƒ†ã‚¤ãƒ©ãƒ¼å±•é–‹ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã¯åº§æ¨™åŸç‚¹è¿‘å‚ã«ã®ã¿é›»è·ãƒ»é›»æµåˆ†å¸ƒãŒå­˜åœ¨ã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«å¯¾å¿œã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(\mathbf{r} = (x, y, z), \mathbf{r}_0 = (x_0, y_0, z_0)\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
R 
&amp;= |\mathbf{r} - \mathbf{r}_0| 
= \sqrt{x^2 \left( 1- \frac{x_0}{x} \right) + y^2 \left( 1- \frac{y_0}{y} \right) + z^2 \left( 1- \frac{z_0}{z} \right)} \\
&amp;\simeq \sqrt{x^2 \left( 1-\frac{2x_0}{x}\right) + y^2 \left( 1-\frac{2y_0}{y}\right) + z^2 \left( 1-\frac{2z_0}{z}\right)} 
= \sqrt{r^2 - 2 \mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0} 
= r \sqrt{1-2\frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{r^2}} \\
&amp;\simeq r \left( 1 - \frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{r^2} \right)
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã“ã‚Œã‚ˆã‚Šã€é…å»¶æ™‚åˆ»ã¯</p>

\[t_\mathrm{ret} 
= t-\frac{R}{c} 
\simeq t-\frac{r}{c} + \frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{cr} 
= t_0 + \frac{\mathbf{r}\cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{cr} \tag{3}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¿‘ä¼¼ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚\(t_0\)ã¯åŸç‚¹ã‹ã‚‰æ”¾å°„ãŒã‚ã£ãŸã¨ã—ãŸå ´åˆã®é…å»¶æ™‚åˆ»ã§ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨åŒæ§˜ã«é…å»¶æ™‚åˆ»ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹é›»æµå¯†åº¦ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã¯</p>

\[[ \mathbf{j}] 
= \mathbf{j} (\mathbf{r}_0, t_\mathrm{ret}) 
= \mathbf{j} (\mathbf{r}_0, t_0 + \frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{cr}) 
\simeq \mathbf{j} (\mathbf{r}_0, t_0) + \frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{cr} \left. \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t} \right|_{t=t_0}
= [\mathbf{j}]_0 + \frac{\mathbf{r} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{cr} \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right]_0 \tag{4}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\([\cdots ]_0\)ã¯é…å»¶æ™‚åˆ»\(t_0\)ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹é‡ã‚’è¡¨ã™è¨˜å·ã§ã™ã€‚ãã‚Œã§ã¯åŒæ¥µå­æ”¾å°„ã‹ã‚‰è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚<br />
ã“ã®ç³»ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹é›»æ°—åŒæ¥µå­ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ¡ãƒ³ãƒˆã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{p} = \iiint dV \mathbf{r}_0 \rho(\mathbf{r}_0, t_0) \tag{5}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ä¸¡è¾ºã‚’æ™‚é–“å¾®åˆ†ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{\partial \mathbf{p}}{\partial t} 
= \iiint dV \mathbf{r}_0 \left. \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} \right|_{t=t_0} 
= - \iiint dV \mathbf{r}_0 (\nabla_{\mathbf{r}_0} \cdot \mathbf{j} )\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚é€”ä¸­ã€<a href="/astroelec/heaviside_feynman_jefimenko">é›»è·åˆ†å¸ƒã¨é›»æµåˆ†å¸ƒã«å¯¾ã™ã‚‹é€£ç¶šã®å¼</a>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚å³è¾ºã®ç©åˆ†ã¯ã€éƒ¨åˆ†ç©åˆ†ãªã©ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦å…·ä½“çš„ã«è¨ˆç®—ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\iiiint dV \frac{\partial j_x}{\partial x_0} x_0 
= \iiint dx_0 dy_0 dz_0 \frac{\partial j_x}{\partial x_0} x_0 
= \iint dy_0 dz_0 \left( [j_x x_0]_{-\infty}^\infty - \int_{-\infty}^\infty j_x dx_0 \right) 
= - \iiint dx_0 dy_0 dz_0 j_x\]

\[\iiiint dV \frac{\partial j_y}{\partial y_0} x_0 
= \iiint dx_0 dy_0 dz_0 \frac{\partial j_y}{\partial y_0} x_0 
= \iint dx_0 dz_0 x_0 [j_y ]_{-\infty}^\infty 
= 0\]

<p>ãªã©ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚é€”ä¸­ã€ç„¡é™é ã§ã®è¡¨é¢ç©åˆ†ã¯0ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’ä½¿ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã“ã‚Œã‚‰ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{\partial \mathbf{p}}{\partial t} 
= \iiint \mathbf{j}(\mathbf{r}_0, t_0) dV \tag{6}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚(1), (4), (6)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Šã€é›»æµå¯†åº¦ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’å±•é–‹ã—ãŸã¨ãã®0æ¬¡æˆåˆ†ã‹ã‚‰å‡ºã‚‹é›»ç£æ”¾å°„ã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{E} = \frac{1}{c^2 R} \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{p}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 \times \mathbf{n} \right) \times \mathbf{n} \tag{7}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚æœ€å¾Œã®è¨ˆç®—å¼ã§ã¯\(\mathbf{n} = \frac{\mathbf{r} - \mathbf{r}_0}{\vert \mathbf{r} - \mathbf{r}_0 \vert} \simeq \frac{\mathbf{r}}{r}\)ã¨ã—ã¦ã€ç©åˆ†ã®å¤–ã«å‡ºã—ã¦è¨ˆç®—ã‚’è¡Œã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ç£æ°—åŒæ¥µå­æˆåˆ†ã¨é›»æ°—å››é‡æ¥µæ”¾å°„">ç£æ°—åŒæ¥µå­æˆåˆ†ã¨é›»æ°—å››é‡æ¥µæ”¾å°„</h2>

<p>(1), (2)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š\(\mathbf{E} = \mathbf{B} \times \mathbf{n}\)ã‚ˆã‚Šã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã§ã¯ç£å ´ã‚’å¤‰å½¢ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚(4)å¼ã®\(\left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right]\)ã®é …ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹é›»ç£æ”¾å°„ã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{B} 
= \frac{1}{c^2 R} \iiint dV \left(\frac{\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0}{c} \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2} \right]_0 \right) \times \mathbf{n}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚é€”ä¸­\(\mathbf{r} / R = \mathbf{n}\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚\((\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right]_0 = \frac{1}{2} (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right]_0 + \frac{1}{2} (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{j}}{\partial t}\right]_0\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«2ã¤ã«åˆ†ã‘ã€ã•ã‚‰ã«\(\frac{1}{2} \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathrm{j}}{\partial t^2}\right] \cdot \mathrm{n} \right) \mathrm{r}_0 - \frac{1}{2} \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathrm{j}}{\partial t^2}\right] \cdot \mathrm{n} \right) \mathrm{r}_0\)ã‚’è¿½åŠ ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\mathbf{B} 
= \frac{1}{c^3 R} \iiint \frac{1}{2} \left\{ (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2} \right] - \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right] \cdot \mathbf{n}\right) \mathbf{r}_0\right\} \times \mathbf{n} dV + \frac{1}{c^3 R} \iiint \frac{1}{2} \left\{ (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2} \right] + \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right] \cdot \mathbf{n}\right) \mathbf{r}_0\right\} \times \mathbf{n} dV \tag{8}\]

<p>ç¬¬ä¸€é …ã‚’\(\mathbf{B}_\mathrm{M1}\)ã€ç¬¬äºŒé …ã‚’\(\mathbf{B}_\mathrm{E2}\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ãã¾ã™ã€‚ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«æ’ç­‰å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\left( \mathbf{r}_0 \times \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0\right) \times \mathbf{n} 
= (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 - \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2} \right] \cdot \mathbf{n}\right) \mathbf{r}_0\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«ç£æ°—åŒæ¥µå­</p>

\[\mathbf{m} = \frac{1}{2c} \iiint \mathbf{r}_0 \times \mathbf{j} dV \tag{9}\]

<p>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\mathbf{B}_\mathrm{M1}
= \frac{1}{c^2R} \left( \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{m}}{\partial t^2} \right]_0 \times \mathbf{n} \right) \times \mathbf{n} \tag{10}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦\(\mathbf{B}_\mathrm{M1}\)ã¯ç£æ°—åŒæ¥µå­ã®æ™‚é–“å¤‰åŒ–ã«ã‚ˆã‚Šé›»ç£æ”¾å°„æˆåˆ†ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ç¶šã„ã¦\(\mathbf{B}_\mathrm{E2}\)ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ãã®ãŸã‚ã«ä»¥ä¸‹ã®è¨ˆç®—ã‚’è¡Œã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\iiint (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 dV 
= \left\{ \left( \iiint (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 dV \right) \cdot \mathbf{e}_i \right\} \mathbf{e}_i\]

<p>ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’\(\mathbf{a} = a_i \mathbf{e}_i = (\mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{e}_i) \mathbf{e}_i\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€æˆåˆ†ã”ã¨ã«åˆ†å‰²ã—ã¦æ›¸ãä¸‹ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«\(\mathbf{e}_i\)ã¯\(x, y, z\)æ–¹å‘ã®å˜ä½ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã®å˜ä½ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã¯ã€ä¾‹ãˆã°</p>

\[\mathbf{e}_x = \nabla_0 x_0 
= (\frac{\partial x_0}{\partial x_0},\frac{\partial x_0}{\partial y_0},\frac{\partial x_0}{\partial z_0}) = (1, 0, 0)\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¨ˆç®—ã§ãã‚‹ã®ã§ã€\(\mathbf{e}_i = \nabla_0 r_{0, i}\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ãã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[\iiint (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 dV 
= \left\{ \iiint (\mathbf{n}\cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0 (\cdot \nabla r_{0, i}) \right\} \mathbf{e}_i
= \left( \iiint \nabla \cdot \left\{ (\mathbf{n}\cdot \mathbf{r}_0) r_{0, i} \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0\right\} - \iiint r_{0, i} \nabla \cdot \left\{ (\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}_0) \left[ \frac{\partial^2 \mathbf{j}}{\partial t^2}\right]_0\right\} dV\right)\]

